58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(↑R2') (F2)\">(↑R2') (F2)</span></p></td><td colspan=\"5\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"↑B' R2' F\">↑B' R2' F</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"↑R2' U2' F2\">↑R2' U2' F2</span></p></td><td colspan=\"5\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R' F\">F R' F</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' F R'\">R' F R'</span></p></td><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' FB' R\">R' FB' R</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"y R' F D2 R'\">y R' F D2 R'</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"y R' F R U2 L2\">y R' F R U2 L2</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R' U2 F R'\">R' U2 F R'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image160.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"5\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image162.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"5\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image164.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image166.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"↑R' U' R' F\">↑R' U' R' F</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U' R' (F) (U) R2\">U' R' (F) (U) R2</span></p></td><td colspan=\"5\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"↓R U R B'\">↓R U R B'</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U R (B') (U') R2'\">U R (B') (U') R2'</span></p></td><td colspan=\"5\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R B'\">R U' R B'</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U' R' U R2 B'\">U' R' U R2 B'</span></p></td><td colspan=\"4\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"↑R' U R' F\">↑R' U R' F</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U R U' R2' F\">U R U' R2' F</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Cross Tips十字</strong></p><p>判断二棱十字是否已还原</p><p>判断二棱十字相对位置是否正确</p><p><img alt=\"图标\n\n描述已自动生成\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image167.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"图标\n\n描述已自动生成\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image168.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image170.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">        <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image172.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>Only consider cross edges in D, and ignore ADF. Opposite color cross edges are solved iff they are in opposite positions. Adj color cross edges are solved iff they are in correctly adjacent positions.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Correctly Adjacent</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image174.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image176.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image170.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image178.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Bars</p></td><td><p>Opp Bars</p></td><td><p>\\</p></td><td><p>/</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Wrong Adjacent</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image180.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image182.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image184.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image172.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>单棒</p></td><td><p>单棒</p></td><td><p>叉</p></td><td><p>对色叉</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Choice of Color Cross</strong></p><p>Choose easy cross: 选择简单十字:</p><p>1. 4 move or less cross. 4步以内十字.</p><p>2. 2 cross edges using 2 move or less. 2步以内变成2个已还原的十字棱.</p><p>3. 2-gen cross using 2 move or less. 2步以内变成2流十字.</p><p>4. 112 block (to build Xcross). 112砖 (方便做拓展十字).</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Save F2L after Pseudo Cross</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image186.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U R' D) R U' R' / (R U' R' D) R U' R'\">(R U R' D) R U' R' / (R U' R' D) R U' R'</span></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Fix Wrong Cross</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image188.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image190.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Opp Swap</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image192.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Adj Swap</p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U2 M\">M' U2 M</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"y' U2 S R2' S' R2\">y' U2 S R2' S' R2</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M2' U2 M2'\">M2' U2 M2'</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"y S' R2 S\">y S' R2 S</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"S' (U2 M' U' M) S\">S' (U2 M' U' M) S</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R D R' D' R\">R D R' D' R</span></p><p>(break <a href=\"/tutorial/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>)</p></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>减少换手, 结尾尽量中手.</p><p> 十字中心被摆到背面. 初学者可能不习惯这种操作, 他们更会倾向于做十字全程中十字中心始终在底面, 因为这比十字在还原中不固定要更容易理解, 但是这样的可能代价就是十字可能不是OO (速拧最优)的.​</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"r' D2 R D' r\">r' D2 R D' r</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"r' D R' D2 r\">r' D R' D2 r</span></p><p><strong>十字技巧</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image194.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image196.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image198.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image200.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image202.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image204.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>判断二棱十字是否已还原</p><p>判断二棱十字相对位置是否正确</p><p>仅考虑已在底层位置的十字棱, 且不考虑ADF. 对色十字棱已还原当且仅当它们位置相对.邻色十字棱已还原当且仅当它们正确相邻.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>正确相邻</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image174.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image176.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image170.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image178.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>棒</p></td><td><p>对色棒</p></td><td><p>\\</p></td><td><p>/</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>错误相邻</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image180.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image182.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image184.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image172.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>单棒</p></td><td><p>单棒</p></td><td><p>叉</p></td><td><p>对色叉</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Choice of Color Cross 十字底色选择</strong></p><p>Choose easy cross: 选择简单十字:</p><p>1. 4 move or less cross. 4步以内十字.</p><p>2. 2 cross edges using 2 move or less. 2步以内变成2个已还原的十字棱.</p><p>3. 2-gen cross using 2 move or less. 2步以内变成2流十字.</p><p>4. 112 block (to build Xcross). 112砖 (方便做拓展十字).</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Save F2L after Pseudo Cross</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image186.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U R' D) R U' R' / (R U' R' D) R U' R'\">(R U R' D) R U' R' / (R U' R' D) R U' R'</span></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>Fix Wrong Cross</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image188.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image190.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Opp Swap</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/3x3-cross/en/image192.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">Adj Swap</p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U2 M\">M' U2 M</span>